## Parent Issue
#27 - 6.5 Chat Interface + Dashboard UI

## Objective
Create React hook for SSE streaming responses.

## Requirements
- Connect to SSE endpoint
- Handle chunk events
- Handle done/error events
- Progressive text display
- Cleanup on unmount

## Implementation

```typescript
function useStreaming(options: UseStreamingOptions) {
  const [isStreaming, setIsStreaming] = useState(false);
  const [content, setContent] = useState('');

  const startStream = useCallback(async (url: string, body: object, token: string) => {
    // POST to initiate, then connect to SSE
  }, []);

  const stopStream = useCallback(() => {
    // Close EventSource
  }, []);

  return { isStreaming, content, startStream, stopStream };
}
```

## Files to Create
- `frontend/src/hooks/useStreaming.ts`

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] SSE connection established
- [ ] Chunks accumulated progressively
- [ ] Done event completes streaming
- [ ] Error handling works
- [ ] Cleanup on unmount

## Estimated Time
2.5 hours
